		    </td>
		  </tr>
		  <tr>
		    <td width="100%" valign="top" colspan="2"><font face="Verdana" size="2">
			A lizard about or one step up from a Zealot... Cons red to me still at lvl 30. They have a opening spell, maybe its HT, but it drops about 3-1/2 bubbles of life from me, with about 922hps... Nasty thing and definantly need a group. They are located in the 4 Corners area in Cazic and are very rare... Been there about 2 weeks and have seen 4.
		  
		  </font>
